lex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>كَذَٰلِكَ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> يَضۡرِبُ ٱللَّهُ ٱلۡحَقَّ وَٱلۡبَٰطِلَۚ فَأَمَّا ٱلزَّبَدُ فَيَذۡهَبُ </div><div><a data-content='مرميّا به مطروحا أو متفرّقا' tabindex='0' role='button' class='fake-link tafsir' data-toggle='popover' data-placement='top'>جُفَآءٗۖ</a></div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>وَأَمَّا</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> مَا يَنفَعُ ٱلنَّاسَ فَيَمۡكُثُ فِي ٱلۡأَرۡضِۚ كَذَٰلِكَ يَضۡرِبُ </div><div>ٱللَّهُ</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>ٱلۡأَمۡثَالَ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> ٧١ لِلَّذِينَ ٱسۡتَجَابُواْ لِرَبِّهِمُ ٱلۡحُسۡنَىٰۚ وَٱلَّذِينَ لَمۡ </div><div>يَسۡتَجِيبُواْ</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>لَهُۥ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> لَوۡ أَنَّ لَهُم مَّا فِي ٱلۡأَرۡضِ جَمِيعٗا وَمِثۡلَهُۥ مَعَهُۥ لَٱفۡتَدَوۡاْ </div><div>بِهِۦٓۚ</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>أُوْلَٰٓئِكَ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> لَهُمۡ سُوٓءُ ٱلۡحِسَابِ وَمَأۡوَىٰهُمۡ جَهَنَّمُۖ <a data-content='بئس الفراش والمستقر جهنّم' tabindex='0' role='button' class='fake-link tafsir' data-toggle='popover' data-placement='top'>وَبِئۡسَ ٱلۡمِهَادُ</a> </div><div>٨١</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'></div>",
